#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:2
msgid "术语"
msgstr "Terminology"

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:5
msgid "mDNS"
msgstr "mDNS"

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:6
msgid ""
"Multicast DNS (mDNS)，多播DNS，使用5353端口，组播地址为 ``224.0.0.251`` 或 "
"``[FF02::FB]`` "
"。在一个没有常规DNS服务器的小型网络内可以使用mDNS来实现类似DNS的编程接口、包格式和操作语义。mDNS协议的报文与DNS的报文结构相同，但有些字段对于mDNS来说有新的含义。"
msgstr ""
"Multicast DNS (mDNS) uses port 5353 and the multicast address "
"``224.0.0.251`` or ``[FF02::FB]``. In a small network without a conventional "
"DNS server, mDNS can provide DNS-like programming interfaces, packet formats, "
"and operational semantics. mDNS packets use the same structure as DNS "
"packets, but some fields have new meanings in mDNS."

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:8
msgid "启动mDNS的主机会在进入局域网后向所有主机组播消息，包含主机名、IP等信息，其他拥有相应服务的主机也会响应含有主机名和IP的信息。"
msgstr ""
"After a host with mDNS enabled joins a LAN, it multicasts messages to all "
"hosts containing information such as its host name and IP address. Other "
"hosts that provide the corresponding services also respond with information "
"containing their host names and IP addresses."

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:10
msgid "mDNS的域名是用 ``.local`` 和普通域名区分开的。"
msgstr "mDNS domain names are distinguished from ordinary domain names by ``.local``."

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:13
msgid "FQDN"
msgstr "FQDN"

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:14
msgid ""
"FQDN (Fully-Qualified Domain Name) 是域名的完全形态，主要是包含零长度的根标签，例如 "
"``www.example.com.`` 。"
msgstr ""
"An FQDN (Fully-Qualified Domain Name) is the complete form of a domain name. "
"It mainly includes the zero-length root label, for example "
"``www.example.com.``."

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:17
msgid "TLD"
msgstr "TLD"

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:18
msgid "Top-Level Domain (TLD) 是属于根域的一个域，例如 ``com`` 或 ``jp`` 。"
msgstr "A Top-Level Domain (TLD) is a domain under the root, such as ``com`` or ``jp``."

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:20
msgid ""
"TLD一般可以分为 Country Code Top-Level Domains (ccTLDs) 、Generic Top-Level "
"Domains (gTLDs) 以及其它。"
msgstr ""
"TLDs are generally divided into Country Code Top-Level Domains (ccTLDs), "
"Generic Top-Level Domains (gTLDs), and others."

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:23
msgid "IDN"
msgstr "IDN"

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:24
msgid "Internationalized Domain Names for Applications (IDNA) 是为了处理非ASCII字符的情况。"
msgstr ""
"Internationalized Domain Names for Applications (IDNA) is designed to handle "
"non-ASCII characters."

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:27
msgid "CNAME"
msgstr "CNAME"

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:28
msgid "CNAME即Canonical name，又称alias，将域名指向另一个域名。"
msgstr ""
"CNAME stands for canonical name, also known as an alias, and points one "
"domain name to another."

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:31
msgid "TTL"
msgstr "TTL"

#: ../../source/network/domain/terminology.rst:32
msgid "Time To Live，无符号整数，记录DNS记录过期的时间，最小是0，最大是2147483647 (2^31 - 1)。"
msgstr ""
"Time To Live is an unsigned integer that records when a DNS record expires. "
"The minimum value is 0, and the maximum value is 2147483647 (2^31 - 1)."
